Package: mirDIP
Type: Package
Title: R Client for the mirDIP Web API
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Jaime", family = "Falcon", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
           email = "jaime.falcon@example.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000")))
Description: A lightweight R client to query the mirDIP web service
    for unidirectional and bidirectional searches of gene symbols and
    microRNAs. The mirDIP database provides comprehensive microRNA-target
    interactions with confidence scores. This package provides convenient
    R functions to query the API and parse responses into R data structures.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/jaimefalcon/mirDIP
BugReports: https://github.com/jaimefalcon/mirDIP/issues
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    httr,
    utils
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    BiocStyle,
    BiocManager
biocViews: Software, GeneTarget, MicroRNA, Network, DataImport
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Config/testthat/edition: 3
SystemRequirements: Internet connection for API access